#. 1: raw
msgctxt "DeathMountain_00"
msgid ""
"Scorching Climates<1.ra>In the extreme heat of volcanic regions, wooden "
"bows or shields\n"
"you have equipped will catch fire. It's better to use metal equipment\n"
"instead."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "DeathMountain_01"
msgid ""
"Scorching Climates<1.ra>The extreme temperatures of volcanic regions will"
" hurt you without\n"
"the proper precautions. Wear fireproof equipment or down an elixir\n"
"to stave off the heat."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Field_01"
msgid ""
"Rumor has it...<1.ra>Forest spirits called Koroks like to hide in "
"unexpected spots. Never\n"
"pass up an opportunity to investigate things that look out of place!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Field_02"
msgid ""
"Rumor has it...<1.ra>Deep in the forest resides a glowing blue spirit in "
"the form of\n"
"a rabbit. It is said that whoever is skilled enough to hit it with an\n"
"arrow receives a handsome reward."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Field_03"
msgid ""
"Smoke Signals<1.ra>A plume of smoke in the distance is a good sign that "
"you might\n"
"find someone at its origin."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Field_04"
msgid ""
"Shooting Stars<1.ra>If you should see a star shoot through the night sky,"
" mark the place\n"
"where it landsâ€”you might find something there."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Gerudo_00"
msgid ""
"Sand Seals<1.ra>In order to hitch a ride behind a sand seal, you'll first"
" need to\n"
"equip a shield."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Gerudo_01"
msgid ""
"Sand Seals<1.ra>Sand seals provide a fast way to travel across sand. When"
" hitching \n"
"a ride, be careful not to run into any rocks!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Gerudo_02"
msgid ""
"Sand Seals<1.ra>These large beasts native to the Gerudo Desert are much "
"friendlier\n"
"than they look. They've been domesticated over time for use as a\n"
"mode of transportation."
msgstr ""

